---
title: Easy Rosemary Lamb Fusilli with Balsamic Tomato Salad
description: This simple yet sumptuous dish is absolute decadence from start to finish. From the rich, rosemary-infused lamb mince to the
'al dente' fusilli and delightfully sharp balsamic salad. It'll be both ready and eaten in record time!
